{"id":645966,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/06/【立此存照】i-cant-tweet/","date":"2020-06-01T07:32:45Z","modified":"2020-06-02T05:32:14Z","title":"【立此存照】I can&#8217;t tweet","content":"<p>5月30日，环球网官方微博发布消息报道“全美超30城骚乱”相关新闻，并将中国外交部发言人华春莹的一条讥讽推文“I can&#8217;t breathe”加以引用（黑人弗洛伊德遭警方暴力执法时的求救语）：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/环球网.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-645967\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/环球网.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"565\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/环球网.png 946w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/环球网-239x300.png 239w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/环球网-815x1024.png 815w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/环球网-768x964.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">&quot;I can&#39;t breathe.&quot; <a href=\"https://t.co/UXHgXMT0lk\">pic.twitter.com/UXHgXMT0lk</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Hua Chunying 华春莹 (@SpokespersonCHN) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SpokespersonCHN/status/1266741986096107520?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">May 30, 2020</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>不少网民对官方自由引用墙外资讯和集中式的选择性报道表示不满，纷纷回应“I cant’t tweet”。这些回复疑似已遭到审查和控评，目前在<a href=\"https://weibo.com/1686546714/J4ndJCkOK\">该条微博</a>下搜索相关内容已无显示。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/环球网.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-645968\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/环球网.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"573\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/环球网.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/环球网-235x300.jpg 235w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/环球网-804x1024.jpg 804w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/环球网-768x978.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>当然，这也并非网友第一次因官方媒体引用墙外“推特言论”而表示不满：</p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"qaTfPRzyNV\"><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/05/%e3%80%90%e7%bd%91%e7%bb%9c%e6%b0%91%e8%ae%ae%e3%80%91%e6%88%91%e4%bb%ac%e4%b9%9f%e6%83%b3%e4%b8%8e%e4%b8%96%e7%95%8c%e5%90%84%e5%9b%bd%e4%ba%ba%e6%b0%91%e5%a2%9e%e8%bf%9b%e6%84%9f%e6%83%85/\">【网络民议】“我们也想与世界各国人民增进感情呀”</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><iframe title=\"《【网络民议】“我们也想与世界各国人民增进感情呀”》—中国数字时代\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/05/%e3%80%90%e7%bd%91%e7%bb%9c%e6%b0%91%e8%ae%ae%e3%80%91%e6%88%91%e4%bb%ac%e4%b9%9f%e6%83%b3%e4%b8%8e%e4%b8%96%e7%95%8c%e5%90%84%e5%9b%bd%e4%ba%ba%e6%b0%91%e5%a2%9e%e8%bf%9b%e6%84%9f%e6%83%85/embed/#?secret=qaTfPRzyNV\" data-secret=\"qaTfPRzyNV\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"w9gopVjioW\"><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/05/%e6%b3%95%e5%b9%bf-%e5%8f%aa%e8%ae%b8%e5%b7%9e%e5%ae%98%e5%8f%91tweet%e3%80%80%e4%b8%8d%e8%ae%b8%e7%99%be%e5%a7%93%e7%bf%bb%e5%a2%99-%e6%b8%af%e5%aa%92%e6%8c%87/\">法广 | 只许州官“发Tweet”　不许百姓“翻墙” 港媒指防火墙争议</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><iframe title=\"《法广 | 只许州官“发Tweet”　不许百姓“翻墙” 港媒指防火墙争议》—中国数字时代\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/05/%e6%b3%95%e5%b9%bf-%e5%8f%aa%e8%ae%b8%e5%b7%9e%e5%ae%98%e5%8f%91tweet%e3%80%80%e4%b8%8d%e8%ae%b8%e7%99%be%e5%a7%93%e7%bf%bb%e5%a2%99-%e6%b8%af%e5%aa%92%e6%8c%87/embed/#?secret=w9gopVjioW\" data-secret=\"w9gopVjioW\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","author":1069,"categories":[18271,38827,38912,39486,39484],"tags":[9526,25837,9249,40280,8604,16068]}